❓ Write a procedure to accept a number from user and check the number is positive, negative or zero. [5 marks]


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE check_number(n INT)
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
BEGIN
    IF n > 0 THEN
        RAISE NOTICE 'Positive Number';
    ELSIF n < 0 THEN
        RAISE NOTICE 'Negative Number';
    ELSE
        RAISE NOTICE 'Zero';
    END IF;
END;
$$;


---

✅ Call

CALL check_number(10);


